Rust dependencies
-----------------

All crates resolved through crates.io retain their upstream licenses. The
full machine-readable inventory of Rust dependencies and their licenses can be
regenerated with:

    cargo install cargo-about
    cargo about generate cargo/about/about.hbs > docs/third-party-licenses.html

or audited with:

    cargo install cargo-deny
    cargo deny check licenses

